Gopinathpur is a village in Baleswar Sadar subdistrict in Baleswar District in the Indian state of Odisha.  it had a population of 986 in 240 households. The nearest major railway station is the Balasore railway station.
Geography
The village is 3 km from Nilgiri.
Economy
Most of the people depend on cultivation.
